---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DataDisclaimer from '../components/DataDisclaimer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — World Companies by Market Cap"
  description="Privacy Policy for World Companies by Market Cap. Learn how we respect user privacy, handle local storage, and display privacy-safe advertisements."
>
  <DataDisclaimer />

  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-8">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Last updated: July 23, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        At World Companies by Market Cap (worldcompaniesmarketcap.com), accessible from https://worldcompaniesmarketcap.com, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by World Companies by Market Cap and how we use it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">1. Local Storage Usage</h2>
      <p>
        We do not maintain user accounts or databases containing personally identifiable information (PII). Features such as dark/light mode preference and your personal stock watchlist are stored strictly inside your browser's local storage (`localStorage`).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">2. Log Files</h2>
      <p>
        World Companies by Market Cap follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit websites. All hosting services do this as a part of hosting services' analytics. The information collected by log files includes internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date and time stamp, referring/exit pages, and possibly the number of clicks.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">3. Advertising Partners</h2>
      <p>
        Third-party ad servers or ad networks use technologies like cookies, JavaScript, or Web Beacons that are used in their respective advertisements and links that appear on World Companies by Market Cap. They automatically receive your IP address when this occurs.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">4. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at privacy@worldcompaniesmarketcap.com.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
